author: Kit Holden For Mailonline
title: Borussia Dortmund seek Champions League relief v Benfica | Daily Mail Online
text: Missing Mats Hummels, a ranting coach and inconsistent form: Borussia Dortmund desperately need European relief against Benfica Borussia Dortmund are enduring a Bundesliga campaign to forget They beat RB Leipzig and Bayern in the league but fell to lowly Darmstadt Thomas Tuchel's side will hope to find respite in their Champions League tie The play Portuguese outfit Benfica for a place in the quarter-final Sportsmail takes a look at what has happened to one of Europe's powerhouses
